<p class="">The "Daring" sank in 30 seconds.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d32e5bae-4587-48b7-9c3c-f3e0c8b417a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
