<p class="">I made a further appeal in regard to financial support for the training of small boys.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b2715e8e-f0be-4797-a727-9fdbaa4e407a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
